dct_title_s: City of Manhattan or New York
dct_description_sm: Covers lower Manhattan. Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Facsimile. In lower margin: From the collection of charts and plans made by order of the Duke de Choiseul and executed by S. Bellin in 1764. In lower margin: Lith for D.T. Valentine's Manual, for 1861. Includes index to points of interest.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : Common Council, 1861] (N[ew] Y[ork] : Geo. Hayward)
